If people have Macs with wireless access, they can get connectivity in
the Engineering library or the Second floor of Evans... to use the
AirBears service all they have to do is be able to detect the network,
open a web browser window and enter their CalNet ID and passphrase...
not as quick as local DHCP but sufficient.

Joe

